OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FThe United States launched new
OL,7,Fairstrikes against Iran early on
OL,8,FThursday, and Tehran responded by
OL,9,Ftargeting Gulf Arab countries, after
OL,10,FUS President Donald Trump declared
OL,11,Fthat a ceasefire between the nations
OL,12,Fwas "over".
OL,14,FBack-and-forth attacks have repeatedly
OL,15,Fthreatened the ceasefire, but
OL,16,FThursday's appeared bigger all around.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
