CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FSirens sounded at least three times in
OL,7,FBahrain. Missiles targeted Kuwait and
OL,8,FQatar. Sirens sounded on Thursday
OL,9,Fafternoon in Jordan as well, where the
OL,10,FUS has stationed troops and aircraft.
OL,12,FThe strikes came hours after Trump
OL,13,Fsaid recent Iranian attacks on ships
OL,14,Fin the Strait of Hormuz signaled the
OL,15,Fend of a fragile ceasefire and
OL,16,Fthreatened to escalate the conflict if
OL,17,Fthey didn't stop. That raised concerns
OL,18,Fthat the region could tip back into a
OL,19,Fwar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
