CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FThere was no immediate word of damage
OL,7,Fin the Gulf Arab countries, but
OL,8,FKuwait's military said it was actively
OL,9,Fintercepting incoming drones and
OL,10,Fmissiles.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
