PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FUS Central Command (CENTCOM) said it
OL,7,Fhit military targets along Iran's
OL,8,Fcoastline, including air defence
OL,9,Fsystems, coastal surveillance assets,
OL,10,Fmissile and drone storage sites, naval
OL,11,Fcapabilities, and military logistics
OL,12,Finfrastructure.
OL,14,FThe strikes were intended to "further
OL,15,Fdegrade" Iran's ability "to threaten
OL,16,Ffreedom of navigation" in the Strait
OL,17,Fof Hormuz, through which a fifth of
OL,18,Fthe world's oil and natural gas passed
OL,19,Fbefore the war began.
