PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FIranian state media reported
OL,7,Fexplosions in several locations,
OL,8,Fincluding Bushehr, home to Iran's
OL,9,Fnuclear power plant complex, and the
OL,10,Fsouthern port cities of Chabahar,
OL,11,FKonarak, Bandar Abbas and Sirik.
OL,13,F"US forces remain vigilant, lethal,
OL,14,Fand prepared to execute operations
OL,15,Fdirected by the commander in chief," a
OL,16,FCENTCOM statement said.
OL,18,FMore than 20 US Navy warships were
OL,19,Fpatrolling waters across the Middle
OL,20,FEast on Wednesday, CENTCOM added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
