PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FTrump posted several videos on his
OL,7,Fsocial media site of what he said were
OL,8,Fexplosions in Iran and issued another
OL,9,Fwarning to the Islamic Republic after
OL,10,Fleaving a Nato summit in Turkey.
OL,12,FAboard Air Force One, the president
OL,13,Ftold reporters he had received a call
OL,14,Ffrom Iranian leadership and claimed
OL,15,Fthey wanted to make a deal "so badly".
OL,17,FEarlier on Wednesday, he had described
OL,18,FIran as being "evil, sick people", and
OL,19,Fsaid he thought the Memorandum of
OL,20,FUnderstanding, established between the
OL,21,Ftwo countries last month, was "over".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,F"To me, I think it's over. I don't
OL,7,Fwant to deal with them anymore," Trump
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FThe US president also renewed his past
OL,11,Fthreats to hit Iran's civilian
OL,12,Finfrastructure, including electric
OL,13,Fplants and desalination plants, and to
OL,14,Fseize the oil-production hub of Kharg
OL,15,FIsland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
