PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783689573
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange fire after Trump
OL,4,Csays ceasefire is 'over'
OL,6,FThe US first launched strikes on Iran
OL,7,Fafter three tankers were hit close to
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz on Tuesday,
OL,9,Fcausing Iranian forces to retaliate by
OL,10,Ftargeting American military sites in
OL,11,Fthe Persian Gulf.
OL,13,FIran has asserted that the interim
OL,14,Fceasefire deal gives it the right to
OL,15,Fmanage traffic through the strait,
OL,16,Fwith Parliament Speaker Mohammad
OL,17,FBagher Qalibaf, a key negotiator in
OL,18,Fpeace talks, issuing a threat on
OL,19,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
